    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《绣口吐珠》是首款引入了脸部控制技术的打砖块游戏，将嘴巴形状作为小球挡板的实时形状，您需要在摄像头前灵活晃动嘴巴操控挡板去反弹小球，击碎所有砖块以获得胜利。请成为打砖块游戏领域的“嘴强王者”吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237120/extras/50ae1184fbb306a6ec1d0352a53684f3.poster.avif?t=1741879880\" width=800 height=470 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237120/extras/50ae1184fbb306a6ec1d0352a53684f3.webm?t=1741879880\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237120/extras/50ae1184fbb306a6ec1d0352a53684f3.mp4?t=1741879880\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特点</strong> <br> <br>游戏包含8章，每个章节有9个关卡，共72个关卡。    </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18种独特的道具（包含增益效果和减益效果），在沿用传统打砖块类游戏的功能上，加入了许多与嘴巴动作关联的道具效果。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237120/extras/57fcd53c7d141c7f916652fca34ee8a7.avif?t=1741879880\" width=300 height=162 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18种独特的砖块（强度不同，各具特点和功能）。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237120/extras/b7e5f4d099062630e2a4e4d245428adb.avif?t=1741879880\" width=300 height=164 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18种各具功能的机关，玩家可以通过晃动头部，调整鼻子方位以及面部朝向，来操控场景内的各种机关。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237120/extras/cd02799b34accb5b865ecd35fa7d9dd8.avif?t=1741879880\" width=300 height=160 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10种生物（包含Boss）, 本游戏引入生物和Boss设定，为打砖块游戏增添了投掷道具类生物，同时将摩艾石像等作为可挑战Boss。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3237120/extras/519bbef431dac9150a5ef04d16961fef.avif?t=1741879880\" width=300 height=108 /></span></p></li></ul>",
